{
  "text": "I am guessing that the wheels on this chariot indicate the ability of the mind to be able now to move in time/space. Is this correct? I am Ra. We cannot say that the observation is totally incorrect, for there is as much work in time/space as the individual who evokes this complex of concepts has assimilated. However, it would be more appropriate to draw the attention to the fact that although the chariot is wheeled, it is not harnessed to that which draws it by a physical or visible harness. What then, O Student, links and harnesses the chariot's power of movement to the chariot?",
